{"tid":2221082,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［理性討論］我地唔應該當「屌黃圈」係笑話咁睇","createTime":"2020-09-28T06:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T07:22:34.000Z","uid":211994,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf32e0c18af266fa2540f0872da252ba94f13ed","tid":2221082,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"<em>樓主嘅資料來源：某啲手足開嘅tg channel（自己搵），Terry Yeung Blog<br />\n</em><br />\n我地都知道，黃圈係以經濟打擊共產黨嘅資金來源，同為日後長期抗爭做一個準備（如有錯煩請指正）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>然而，唔計中共大外宣，有一班勇武前線係真心覺得黃圈助用唔大、廢</strong><br />\n<br />\n有一班手足一個禮拜生活費只有幾十蚊<br />\n佢地一個禮拜都係食公仔麵同出前一丁，一日有兩餐已經叫好<br />\n佢地冇護照/見光死而冇得搵工<br />\n喺屋企捱杯麵之餘，又要健身同買野個陣<br />\n佢地見到一班相對犧牲冇咁大嘅人<br />\n用四五六十蚊食一餐黃店<br />\n唔駛驚會有一日俾人滅口<br />\n仲叫班前線「去打工啦<br />\n咁大個人有手有腳唔係唔做野下話」<br />\n心入面當然唔好過<br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"gold\">我聽過有啲手足係咁講：<br />\n「你幾時見過有一個國家嘅軍人要出去賺錢養自己買裝去打仗？」</span></em><br />\n<br />\n黃圈嘅錢好少會流入前線抗爭者手上<br />\n正確啲講，只有出名嘅人先會到幫助<br />\n<br />\n呢個係邏輯上無解，出名嘅人自然就會安全啲，其他人提供支援嘅風險都低啲<br />\n你可以同人講你patreon有份subscribe黃之鋒沈旭暉<br />\n但你唔會想有人知你今日助養咗邊一位無名嘅抗爭者，一有人知，到時就齊齊監倉見<br />\n隨時間推移，有名氣嘅人得到嘅資源越滾越大<br />\n冇名氣嘅，死咗都冇人知<br />\n<br />\n我唔係指責有名氣嘅抗爭者/提供支援咁多位家長，只係描述現況<br />\n<br />\n咁要點做呢，自己諗，自己搵<br />\n<br />\n其實我都係拾人牙慧，想知多少少可以睇下呢篇文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFjhrFKnlHa/?igshid=10vu4qalyt3vn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFjhrFKnlHa%2F%3Figshid%3D10vu4qalyt3vn&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=bb07dee1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFjhrFKnlHa%2F%3Figshid%3D10vu4qalyt3vn&h=58407be3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CFjhrFKnlHa/?igshid=10vu4qalyt3vn</a>"},{"pid":"8bc72a59428bc9a1dd4a084ecade2a1061c4581c","tid":2221082,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d694ec2d2125edda269040e6c204fb4b2c0b56f","tid":2221082,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:31:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24a4f027454e32fee1fdfdb44d1b5bf1f5d8f18d","tid":2221082,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:35:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2bb95c316611adc71af933a031e5f2df132d5a9","tid":2221082,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:35:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f90ef4b212d292a2d6d48b02224190c3a4b1d646","tid":2221082,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:35:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2187c704d039997bcac3315c6eb4a15b46382b0e","tid":2221082,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71c64edda31f6f6844955dbcd78f3e862b802e7","tid":2221082,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8038c621c920a81104a6f94366699fa6980a78","tid":2221082,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"Terry自己都話這種迷思永遠解不開"},{"pid":"25ef48745f12c6b06bd1114aed61b623d982c6c2","tid":2221082,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"除左幫襯黃店（唔止食黃店），其實仲有好多野可以做"},{"pid":"b2c54e9a3d136a9b45998482fc31fa2857d9821c","tid":2221082,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"又鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f3c8db7c614d1105968765fb08bdff956afc55","tid":2221082,"uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d8038c621c920a81104a6f94366699fa6980a78","tid":2221082,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"Terry自己都話這種迷思永遠解不開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"所以唔應該只集中喺黃圈<br />\n只要有喺其他地方支援手足，手足自然唔會話黃圈同撐黃圈"},{"pid":"0b819e5f812e9cda5de0622840d04427ab40fa51","tid":2221082,"uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2c54e9a3d136a9b45998482fc31fa2857d9821c","tid":2221082,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"又鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:22:34.000Z","msg":"冇鬥呀，只係講返依家到底幫到手足幾多，應該點做先好"}]}